comment: Gortat (WAS) sets the screen on Payton (ORL), giving him a step and then absorbing contact.
Vucevic (ORL) does not get to Beal's (WAS) direct path before the contact.
RHH shows Hezonja's (ORL) contact is incidental to his effort to play Beal (WAS) and he does not dislodge him from his position.
Harris (ORL) makes contact with Gortat's (WAS) arm and the contact affects his shot.
L-Slash shows Wall (WAS) cleanly strips the ball from Hezonja (ORL).
RATR shows Vucevic (ORL) makes incidental contact with Porter's (WAS) arm after he follows through.
WAS is not ready to resume play when the time-out clock reaches 00:00.
Wall (WAS) commits a take foul on Harris (ORL).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the officials determined the ball was not in the cylinder and the ruling on the floor was overturned.
[Observable in enhanced video] Vucevic (ORL) splits his feet on the perimeter.
